                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830604-27-defend311 t17830604-27-punish146"></join>
               publicly whipped and discharged
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
